
				  Net::Zemanta
				  ============


Net::Zemanta is a Perl interface to services provided by Zemanta.

Zemanta is building a platform for assisted on-line content production.
The system analyses the content and returns suggested images, smart links,
keywords and relevant related stories from the Internet.

See http://zemanta.com for more information.

This module currently allows you to use the Suggest service and retrieve user
configuration for the service.


Installation
============

To install this module run the following commands:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


Dependencies
============

  libwww-perl
  JSON


